// Kodex Flags
// Review and resolve topic flags (outdated, incorrect, incomplete, missing).
// Searchable list with status filter; supports resolving or dismissing open flags.

FUNCTION FlagTypeBadge(type)
  Render a colored badge for the flag type (outdated/incorrect/incomplete/missing).

---

FUNCTION StatusBadge(status)
  Render a colored badge for the flag status (open/resolved/dismissed).

---

FUNCTION Flags()                                                        EXPORT
  CALLS: listFlags (kodex-api), updateFlagStatus (kodex-api)
  Read selectedProject from kodexStore.
  On mount (or project change): load all flags via kodexApi.listFlags.
  Maintain filter state (default: 'open') and a search query.
  Compute filteredFlags by applying the status filter and search query (matches topicName, description, or type).
  On resolve (handleResolve): call kodexApi.updateFlagStatus with 'resolved', then reload.
  On dismiss (handleDismiss): call kodexApi.updateFlagStatus with 'dismissed', then reload.
  Render each flag with its topic link, type badge, status badge, description, dates, and resolve/dismiss actions.
